<div class="text-center p-5  border-t border-brand-secondary/20 flex flex-col gap-4">
<h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-primary text-brand-secondary tracking-[-0.03em] leading-normal font-bold lg:px-60 reveal-on-scroll">
    Right now, I'm learning how small bits work together to build a system — both Design and Development
</h1>

<div class="w-full lg:px-30">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    
    <div class="aspect-square border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-brand-bg/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between items-start text-left rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-secondary/20 group">
      <span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.15em] text-brand-secondary/40 uppercase">
        [ foundations // 01 ]
      </span>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-accent font-bold tracking-tight text-brand-secondary group-hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors duration-300">
          Low-Level Systems
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-brand-secondary/50 font-secondary font-light leading-relaxed">
          Deconstructing memory structures, pointer mechanics, and fundamental data paradigms in C.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="aspect-square border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-brand-bg/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between items-start text-left rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-secondary/20 group">
      <span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.15em] text-brand-secondary/40 uppercase">
        [ architecture // 02 ]
      </span>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-accent font-bold tracking-tight text-brand-secondary group-hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors duration-300">
          Component Models
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-brand-secondary/50 font-secondary font-light leading-relaxed">
          Analyzing state flow, shadow DOM rendering pipelines, and modular UI patterns in React.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="aspect-square border border-brand-secondary/10 bg-brand-bg/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between items-start text-left rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-secondary/20 group">
      <span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.15em] text-brand-secondary/40 uppercase">
        [ visual-logic // 03 ]
      </span>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-accent font-bold tracking-tight text-brand-secondary group-hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors duration-300">
          Interface Interface Anatomy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-brand-secondary/50 font-secondary font-light leading-relaxed">
          Bridging layout geometry, custom typography hierarchies, and hardware-accelerated animations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


</div>
